<!-- "Make item" recipes (СЏв”‚Рїв•ЄРїв•џСЏв”‚СЏв”ЊРїв•ЈСЏв”ЂРїв•¦СЏв”ЊСЏв–„/Рїв•ЎСЏв–ЂРїв•ЁРїв•¬Рїв•ЎРїв•џСЏв”ЊСЏв–„/СЏв”‚СЏв”¬Рїв•¦СЏв”ЊСЏв–„ ...).
     Each recipe: a crafting skill (ESkill token), the crafted item vnum, and up to
     3 ingredient parts. An ingredient: vnum + min_weight + min_power (the minimums
     the supplied component must meet). Add locked="true" to disable a recipe.
     The full production recipe set lives outside the repo; this is a sample. -->
<item_creation>
	<recipe skill="kMakeBow" result="1500">
		<ingredient vnum="1400" min_weight="10" min_power="5"/>
		<ingredient vnum="1428" min_weight="1" min_power="5"/>
	</recipe>
</item_creation>
